Dear voters, dear komodo hodlers,

If my candidacy as NN is SH region is accepted, 20% of mining rewards will go to CHIPS devlopment, 20% will go to #kmdlabs and I will support and help KMD ecosystem and DEX (tools, stats, dockerfiles, block explorers, mining pools and pools with profit switch).
